{"tid":788420,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"低智騎呢「Kiki Challenge」","createTime":"2018-08-21T12:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T00:57:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6b2504b31e459065cd3c7885bda24df660a2f7","tid":788420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180821/20480748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F20480748&d=S8QnQbGsTr4p9EbuerVbS26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=adaff65a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F20480748&h=5f129521\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180821/20480748</a><br />\n<br />\n低智騎呢「Kiki Challenge」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180821/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180821%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=50996b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n近期網上潮玩的「Kiki Challenge」，最初是網絡紅人Shiggy以《In My Feelings》歌曲為背景音樂，對着靜止鏡頭表演原創舞步，引起明星藝人及網民模仿，不知如何還有「升級版」（又即「冒險版」），是舞者開了車門落地跳舞，駕駛者需慢駛來遷就之，方便拍片放上網，挑戰「互動」感。<br />\n<br />\n某港姐候選「佳麗」，為博出位在社交平台上載其在行人路上搔首弄姿絲帶舞，司機慢駛拍攝，尾段她隨手扔掉絲帶在路邊，跳上車裝萌扮可愛──此片段被網民鬧爆：一來亂拋垃圾；二來危及道路安全。<br />\n<br />\n年年都有一堆面目模糊的女子參加選美，沒什麼個性、特色、形象，故以為「出奇制勝」可吸睛，誰知以數度落淚、道歉收場，也算引起注意，後來她更在台上重跳絲帶舞&hellip;&hellip;人人都似小學雞。<br />\n<br />\n其實網上的騎呢片段更好笑。不少玩命的犯禁者，以為好威威，但忘情舞蹈，發生不少意外。由於全球各地都有低智跟風者，所以片段是集大成的：有步履不穩踉蹌倒地；有趕不及上車開不到車門跌個四腳朝天；撞上電燈柱；被劫匪搶車；被眼火爆的路人扔落海；被路過的車撞倒痛苦大喊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n十分精彩。無人同情，活該！  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n別人的小孩 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n抓緊榴槤最後的尾巴 (鄧達智)"},{"pid":"3e62c631b753ce32838cca95bf7ead0419534bbe","tid":788420,"uid":52122,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"今年個個港姐都好撚樣衰<br />\n有啲直頭連廣東話都未講得好<br />\n樣又無 智慧又無 你老母係我就直頭cut撚左佢算啦"},{"pid":"79433397f0f7d1e3eeb40c47a23038f3d97b86e2","tid":788420,"uid":192176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"Kiki do you love me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37fe76930e77192591ad639e7368bca372d85f3","tid":788420,"uid":1300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79433397f0f7d1e3eeb40c47a23038f3d97b86e2","tid":788420,"uid":192176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"Kiki do you love me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"Are you riding?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d78a91340ddfe42ee24dee8c5c45570e8852bb2","tid":788420,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37fe76930e77192591ad639e7368bca372d85f3","tid":788420,"uid":1300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79433397f0f7d1e3eeb40c47a23038f3d97b86e2","tid":788420,"uid":192176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"Kiki do you love me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h